flowchart TD
  A[Signed-in person visits /federation-hub] --> B[FederationHubPolicy#show? -- true for anyone signed in]
  B --> C[PersonalContentSummaryService]
  C --> D[Federatable.included_in_models -- Post, Page, Event]
  D --> E[Counts by federation_visibility + 5 most recent items]
  E --> F[_my_content_panel.html.erb -- always rendered]

  B --> G{FederationHubPolicy#manage_connections_section?}
  G -->|manage_network_connections or approve_network_connections| H[ConnectionHealthSummaryService]
  G -->|neither| K[Admin section hidden]
  H --> I[PlatformConnectionSyncTracking predicates + status counts]
  I --> J[_connection_health_card.html.erb -- links out to Host Dashboard review]

  F --> L[/federation-hub/activity link/]
  J --> L
  L --> M[FederationHub::ActivityFeedService]
  M --> N[Person's own content Activity rows]
  M --> O{include_admin_feed?}
  O -->|Yes| P[+ PlatformConnection sync Activity rows]
  N --> Q[Kaminari-paginated, filterable feed]
  P --> Q
